</a> </h5>
<div class="tagline">
<a href="/dma-driven-neopixels">
NeoPixels and interrupts living in peace and harmony!
</a> </div>
<div class="author">by
<a href="/users/pburgess">
<span class="name">Phillip Burgess</span>
</a> </div>
</div>
</div>
<a href="/dma-driven-neopixels">
<video class="img img-responsive guide-video" preload="auto" muted="muted" loop="loop" autoplay="autoplay" poster="https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/guides/images/000/001/702/medium640thumb/neopixel-ring-anim.gif?1499495177">
