<h5>
<a href="/circuit-playground-express-dac-hacks">
Circuit Playground Express (&amp; other ATSAMD21 Boards) DAC Hacks<br>
</a> </h5>
<div class="tagline">
<a href="/circuit-playground-express-dac-hacks">
Revisiting the Olde Days of television and radio
</a> </div>
<div class="author">by
<a href="/users/pburgess">
<span class="name">Phillip Burgess</span>
</a> </div>
</div>
</div>
<a href="/circuit-playground-express-dac-hacks">
<video class="img img-responsive guide-video" preload="auto" muted="muted" loop="loop" autoplay="autoplay" poster="https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/guides/images/000/001/646/medium640thumb/ntsc-big-anim.gif?1495328829">
