Modern upgrade to a classic maker project
</a> </div>
<div class="author">by
<a href="/users/pburgess">
<span class="name">Phillip Burgess</span>
</a> </div>
</div>
</div>
<a href="/usb-rechargeable-mini-solder-fume-extractor">
<video class="img img-responsive guide-video" preload="auto" muted="muted" loop="loop" autoplay="autoplay" poster="https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/guides/images/000/001/241/medium640thumb/thumbnail-anim.gif?1455414034">
