<div class="title">
<h5>
<a href="/lightship-led-animation-over-wifi">
LIGHTSHIP: LED Animation over WiFi<br>
</a> </h5>
<div class="tagline">
<a href="/lightship-led-animation-over-wifi">
Any sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic.
</a> </div>
<div class="author">by
<a href="/users/pburgess">
<span class="name">Phillip Burgess</span>
</a> </div>
</div>
</div>
<a href="/lightship-led-animation-over-wifi">
<video class="img img-responsive guide-video" preload="auto" muted="muted" loop="loop" autoplay="autoplay" poster="https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/guides/images/000/001/225/medium640thumb/opc-thumbnail.gif?1454222268">
<source src="https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/guides/images/000/001/225/medium640mp4/opc-thumbnail.mp4?1454222268">
<source src="https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/guides/images/000/001/225/medium640webm/opc-thumbnail.webm?1454222268" type="video/webm; codecs=vp8,vorbis">
Your browser does not support the video tag.
</video>
</a> <div class="details">
<div class="description">
<a href="/lightship-led-animation-over-wifi">
Use the Adafruit Feather M0 WiFi board and DotStar LEDs to create mobile luminous art pieces — one or many — synchronized from your computer via wireless networking.
</a> </div>
</div>
